OL,3,CCornwall firefighters not prepared for
OL,4,Cmajor incidents, inspectors say
OL,6,FCornwall Fire and Rescue Service isn't
OL,7,Fprepared for major and multi-agency
OL,8,Fincidents, such as a terrorist attack,
OL,9,Finspectors say.
OL,11,FA state inspector visited the county
OL,12,Fand said it needed to improve in most
OL,13,Fof the inspection categories.
OL,15,FCornwall has the highest number of
OL,16,Ffull-time equivalent firefighters per
OL,17,F1,000 population, due to the number of
OL,18,Fon-call firefighters.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
