OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1781885473
OL,3,CCornwall firefighters not prepared for
OL,4,Cmajor incidents, inspectors say
OL,6,FIn her report, inspector Kathryn Stone
OL,7,FOBE said the service was "keeping
OL,8,Fpeople safe and secure from fire and
OL,9,Fother risks".
OL,11,FHowever, there was a "lack of clear
OL,12,Fdirection and performance management",
OL,13,Fshe said.
OL,15,F"We saw community risk management plan
OL,16,Fpriorities not being met and some
OL,17,Fstaff not being appropriately trained
OL,18,Ffor their roles," she added.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
