OL,3,CCornwall firefighters not prepared for
OL,4,Cmajor incidents, inspectors say
OL,6,FShe also said that, although the
OL,7,Fservice had targeted safety checks at
OL,8,Fthe most vulnerable, it didn't
OL,9,Fcomplete them within the required time
OL,10,Fframe.
OL,12,F"The service needs to do more to
OL,13,Fprepare staff for responding to a
OL,14,Fterrorist incident," she added.
OL,16,FMs Stone highlighted the following
OL,17,Fpoints in her report:
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
