OL,3,CCornwall firefighters not prepared for
OL,4,Cmajor incidents, inspectors say
OL,6,FShe said the service was "good" at
OL,7,Fresponding to fires and emergencies,
OL,8,Fand "adequate" at understanding fire
OL,9,Fand risk, and ensuring public safety
OL,10,Fthrough fire regulation.
OL,12,FHowever, Ms Stone said the following
OL,13,Fareas "required improvement":
OL,15,FKathryn Billing, chief fire officer at
OL,16,FCornwall Fire and Rescue Service,
OL,17,Fsaid: "We welcome this report which
OL,18,Freflects the hard work and dedication
OL,19,Fof the people in our service to make
OL,20,Fthe improvements that have been made.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
