OL,3,CCornwall firefighters not prepared for
OL,4,Cmajor incidents, inspectors say
OL,6,F"However, we recognise that there is
OL,7,Fstill work to do. Our Community Risk
OL,8,FManagement Plan provides the framework
OL,9,Ffor us to continue to improve driven
OL,10,Fby our purpose Serving Cornwall:
OL,11,FProtection, Prevention and Response".
OL,13,FCouncillor Thalia Marrington, cabinet
OL,14,Fmember with responsibility for
OL,15,Fcommunity safety and public protection
OL,16,Fat Cornwall Council, said: "This is a
OL,17,Freally encouraging report and reflects
OL,18,Fthe huge amount of work that has been
OL,19,Fundertaken to improve the service over
OL,20,Fthe last two years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@dO]xD@\OU
