OL,3,CCornwall firefighters not prepared for
OL,4,Cmajor incidents, inspectors say
OL,6,F"We have invested #3million into
OL,7,FCornwall Fire and Rescue Service this
OL,8,Fyear to fund training, and additional
OL,9,Fresources for our fire prevention and
OL,10,Fprotection teams.
OL,12,F"We will continue to support the
OL,13,Fservice as we focus on areas for
OL,14,Fimprovement and ensure the service is
OL,15,Fequipped to protect Cornwall both
OL,16,Ftoday and in years to come."
